cirrussearch-desc: sapihica Elasticsearch kalapalana’an MediaWiki sapikilim sakaluk
cirrussearch-backend-error: izay nanuzuay a munday, la’cus kami pahezek numisyay a kilim. pihalhalen mitanam aca.
cirrussearch-parse-error: la’cus matineng palalitemuh tu kawaw sakacucek, pimadayumay palalitemuh tu kawaw sakacucek. kya palalitemuh tu kawaw amapasulitan apasakapah mikilim  sisetyimo.
cirrussearch-too-busy-error: kilim-inzin makalah ayza. pahalhal satu pitanam aca.
cirrussearch-regex-syntax-error: tatungusay pakatineng a zateng kamu-sakilul mungangaw i $2: $1
cirrussearch-regex-too-busy-error: sayadah tatungusay pakatineng a zateng mikilim saungay imahini miteka, pihalhal sawni mitanam aca
cirrussearch-regex-too-complex-error: sakumceday sakamu tu nizateng-sasakawawen sayadah macibul. pitaayaw [[mw:Special:MyLanguage/Help:CirrusSearch/RegexTooComplex|tina kakitizaan]] matineng hicaen  madayumay akumceday sakamu tu nizateng-sasakawawen.
cirrussearch-now-using: tina Wiki masaungay baluhayay a kilim inzin. ([[mw:Special:MyLanguage/Help:CirrusSearch|matineng ku yadahay]])
cirrussearch-ignored-headings:
#
# i mikilim maydih sekipo a pyawti.
# misumad tina tangan sakalamkam sakay mapasilsilay a kapah pikiliman tu nisulitan miasip a kasabelih pyawti silaheci.
# kapah kisu i mikawaway-kalumyiti caay misumad  lacul kya pacici kasabelih miliyaw kapah pikiliman tu nisulitan miasip.
# kamu-sakilul tinaku isasa’ay:
#   *  amahicahica nay "#" tatebanan nu nisulitan  angangan a silsil tayza izikuzay amihica ku buhci tu kamu.
#   *  amahicahica caay nayi’ ku cacan a silsil dayhiw amisekipo a pyawti。
miazih tu tatenga’ay nasulitan 
hekal masasiket 
aazihan
 #
cirrussearch-boost-templates:
#
#  amahica kasabelih pisaungay tu isasa’ay taazihan mitudung, ngay kya kasabelih a kilim kilac asapicunus setin a sapiwada'-lasubu.
# misumad tinaay silahecitu tansul.
# kamu-sakilul kese tinaku isasa’：
#   *  amahicahica nay "#"  tatebanan nu nisulitan  angangan a silsil ta sazikuzay sapihica ku buhci tu kamu.
#   *  amahicahica caay nayi’ ku cacan silsil sapihica pakatineng pacunus kilac taazihan mitudung kalungangan, yamalyilu pangangananay a salaedan,  tabakiay atu adidi’ay a sulit atu sacahamin tuutuud，izikuzay mangangalep "|" tatebanan nu nisulitan atu cacay cebang asip-bacu, kinacacay mangangalep "%"  tatebanan nu nisulitan.
# kapahay a tinaku：
# Template:Good|150%
# Template:Very Very Good|300%
# Template:Bad|50%
# la’cusay a tinaku：
# Template:Foo|150.234234% <-- caay mahasa pisaungay adidi’ay-asip!
# Foo|150% <--- i sitanengay kapah misaungay, uyzasa amasasiket ta sausi pangangananay a salaedana Foo kasabelih 
# kapah kisu i saayaway sulit cunusen ku boost-templates:"XX" miteka palalitemuh tu kawaw, mitanam setin nu misu, XX sa ku sacahamin amicunus tu kilac taazihan mitudung nu misu，kya nayi’ ku cacan ngay dayhiw mibalic tu silsil tatebanan nu nisulitan.
# pisaungay boost-templates:"XX" a palalitemuh tu kawaw asekipo tina subal a setin lacul.
 #
cirrussearch-pref-desc: kapitanam tu niyam baluhay baziyoung kilim tu sakaluk, midama sayadah a kamu, nipabeli yadah kalamkamay heci atu kapah tu kilim taazihan mitudung labu’ay cudad
cirrussearch-give-feedback: pabelian kami ku hatizaay nabalucu’an nu misu
